data.title: After carrying out large scale education reforms Armenias Vazgen Sargsyan Military Academy applied for and was accepted to join the...
data.meta_description:
236 likes, 6 comments - vermedianetwork on January 10, 2024: "After carrying out large scale education reforms Armenias Vazgen Sargsyan Military Academy applied for and was accepted to join the International Association of Military Academies.

The international association includes 19 military academies from all over the world including from the US, Germany, Kosovo, France, Brazil, South Korea and Qatar. By being a member of the association, the Vazgen Sargsyan Military Academy will be able to carry out student and professor exchanges, join training programs, implement and carry out joint educational and training programs with member academies and take advantage of other benefits offered by the association.".
